                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Meyer</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-05-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 17, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Meyer reports that an imperial ukase was issued on May 17 for restoring the
                    election of nobles in Poland and conferring upon the Poles the right to rent and
                    purchase land, and the minister of the interior is to report ways and means to
                    carry this into effect. Under certain conditions the Lithuanian and Polish
                    languages are permitted in the schools of Poland and more freedom is granted for
                    the use of the Polish language in general.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
